name: Labz' Mayan Slots Soy Candle – Glass Jar Edition
description:
Candlelight, chaos, and calm.
This soy wax candle brings Mayan slots energy into the chill zone. Hand-poured in a reusable glass jar, it’s your low-light go-to for late-night synth runs or power outages.
Natural soy wax
Glass jar with screw-on lid
Subtle, ambient scent
